fields.name: prod3
fields.description:
How To Write Product Descriptions To Grow Sales [Samples Below + Updated in 2021]

Get The Print Version

Tired of scrolling? Download a PDF version for easier offline reading and sharing with coworkers.

Ecommerce managers and online store owners all know the importance of product descriptions. but they are still often overlooked and not optimized to their full potential.

A product description is the marketing copy used to describe a product’s value proposition to potential customers. A compelling product description provides customers with details around features, problems it solves and other benefits to help generate a sale.

fields.name: prod 1
fields.description:
PostgreSQL – Reset Password For Postgres
  • Last Updated : 08 Feb, 2021

In this article, we will look into the step-by-step process of resetting the Postgres user password in case the user forgets it.

PostgreSQL uses the  has a pg_hba.conf configuration file stored in the database data directory (e.g., C:\Program Files\PostgreSQL\12\data on Windows) and is used to handle user authentication. The hba in pg_hba.conf means host-based authentication.

As resetting password requires modification in the pg_hba.conf file, you will need to login to the Postgres role without any password.
